--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This folder contains CobolMac Macro definition files that the CobolMac author
hopes you will find usefull.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

  BITLIB.inc     Macros for the Bit Manipulation Library for COBOL (BITLIB).

  Macros.inc     This file contains the following example macros:

                   %AppendCsv(Field#,CsvRecord#)
                   %JustifyRightLeadZero(InString#,OutString#)
                   %JustifyCenter(InString#,OutString#)
                   %JustifyName(LastName#,FirstName#,MiddleInitial,OutString#)
                   %MoveText(Text#,Destination#,Column#)
                   %MoveNumber(Number#,Destination#,Column#,Format#)

  README         You are reading it.

  sql3i4gc.inc   SQLite3 Interface for GnuCOBOL (Macro Version).

                 Note: This is an ALPHA of version A.00.00.
                       It has been made available for peer review.
                       Please DO NOT use in a Production Environment.

